<h2 style="color: #1A1A1A; margin-top: 0;">Response to Your Inquiry</h2>

<p>Dear {{customerName}},</p>

<p>Thank you for contacting us. Our team has reviewed your message and here is our response:</p>

<div class="info-box">
  <p><span class="label">Subject:</span> {{subject}}</p>
  <p><span class="label">Our Reply:</span></p>
  <p style="margin-top: 4px; white-space: pre-wrap;">{{reply}}</p>
</div>

{{#if originalMessage}}
<p style="margin-top: 16px; padding: 12px; background: #f5f5f5; border-radius: 8px; font-size: 13px; color: #666;">
  <strong>Your original message:</strong><br />
  <span style="white-space: pre-wrap;">{{originalMessage}}</span>
</p>
{{/if}}

<p>If you have further questions, please don't hesitate to reach out to us again.</p>

<p style="text-align: center;">
  <a href="{{storeUrl}}/pages/contact" class="btn-primary">Contact Us Again</a>
</p>

<p>
  Best regards,<br />
  <strong style="color: #D4AF37;">{{businessName}} Team</strong>
</p>
